{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"61eaa22c44","title":"致红军战士与苏区人民电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f547019e3c","index":0,"year":1936,"month":11,"day":20,"articleId":"61eaa22c44"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"97fcf0e473","type":"paragraph","text":"致红军战士与苏区人民电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"61eaa22c44"},{"id":"529c0ed200","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年11月20日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"61eaa22c44"},{"id":"d3cbbfe24e","type":"paragraph","text":"（申）蒋介石此次大举向苏区进攻，不但不许红军抗日，反要消灭红军，消灭苏区人民，命令胡宗南各军向盐池、定边、环县猛政，并要向陕北苏区前进。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"61eaa22c44"},{"id":"3a6d7d965b","type":"paragraph","text":"（乙）我一、二、四方面军会合之后，士气大振，坚决拥护中央与军委之路线，消灭进攻敌人，扩大统一战线，实行抗日救国，于十一月二十一日在定、盐南边之山城堡打了第一个胜仗，消灭胡宗南之一个旅。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"61eaa22c44"},{"id":"d21e57f9fc","type":"paragraph","text":"（丙）这个胜仗是粉碎蒋介石全部进攻的开始，我全体红军战士要更加团结起来，忍苦耐劳，服从命令，勇敢作战。我全苏区人民要帮助红军作战输送粮食，转运伤兵，搬运战利品。白军来时，用坚壁清野对付之。为保卫抗日根据地而战，为扩大抗日根据地而战，为消灭全部进攻之敌人而战。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"61eaa22c44"},{"id":"84face3b87","type":"paragraph","text":"红军万岁！苏维埃万岁！抗日救国之民族革命战争万岁！","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"61eaa22c44"},{"id":"bf0fa943f0","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月二十日","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"61eaa22c44"}],"page":{"id":"22d4521298","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"61eaa22c44","start":9,"end":9}}}},"__N_SSG":true}